Things to pack for camping trip:

Shelter and sleeping:
  Tent with rainfly
  Sleeping bag rated for 40F
  Sleeping pad
  Pillow

Cooking:
  Camp stove and fuel
  Cooler with ice
  Pots and pans
  Utensils and plates
  Trash bags

Clothing:
  Layers for cool evenings
  Rain jacket
  Hiking boots
  Extra socks

Safety:
  First aid kit
  Flashlight with batteries
  Map of the area
  Emergency contacts

Remember to check weather forecast before leaving!
